
## Breaking Change: Please logout and login again to get updated OAuth token from Github, otherwise the app will crash on some tasks.

### Improvements in Windows App:

- Added HockeyApp Integration
- Live Tile Support
- Create and Edit Issues
- Create, edit and delete Repositories
- Edit your User Profile
- Fixed Issue Labels Rendering
- Share issues, repositories and users

### Improvements in Android App:

- Added Splash Screen
- Fixed Back Button Not closing app
- Added HockeyApp Integration
- Fixed crashes on startup
- Updated All ListViews to RecyclerViews
- Refresh available on all pages using Floating Action Button
- Create and Edit Issues
- Create, edit and delete Repositories
- Edit your User Profile
